;                                 $SRCINVERT
;                                 $SRCPAINT
;                                 $WHITENESS
;
; Return values..: Success      - The number of scan lines copied. Note that this value can be negative for mirrored content.
;                  Failure      - 0 and sets the @error flag to non-zero.
; Author.........: Jscript
